Package com.platformer.escape_beyond.model.entity.node.stationary

Class FeatureNode

java.lang.Object
com.platformer.escape_beyond.model.entity.node.stationary.FeatureNode
public class FeatureNode extends Object
A class representing a feature node in the game.

This class associates a specific feature type (e.g., "ice_block", "snow_block") with its corresponding graphical or logical representation as a Node. Feature nodes are used to define game mechanics or environmental effects based on the feature type.
